<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="7" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="6.[264,1323,804,1310]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[320,434,1164,1190]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Remarks</emphasis>
. The original description of 
<taxonomicName authority="Obenberger" authorityName="Obenberger" authorityYear="1935" box="[791,1230,1164,1190]" class="Insecta" family="Buprestidae" genus="Agrilus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="subSpecies" species="tripartitus" subSpecies="japanensis">
<emphasis box="[791,1080,1164,1189]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">A. tripartitus japanensis</emphasis>
Obenberger
</taxonomicName>
neither implies nor requires that there were 
<typeStatus box="[694,800,1204,1230]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">syntypes</typeStatus>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Kurosawa, Y." box="[812,1138,1204,1230]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" pagination="187 - 192" refId="ref17031" refString="Kurosawa, Y. (1989) A list of the buprestid species erroneously described or recorded from Japan. Kanagawa Chuho, 90, 187 - 192." type="journal article" year="1989">Kurosawa (1989: 191–192)</bibRefCitation>
, by mentioning “the type”, validly fixed the 
<typeStatus box="[620,727,1244,1270]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">lectotype</typeStatus>
(ICZN, Article 74.6). The original type locality “ 
<collectingCountry box="[274,346,1284,1310]" name="Japan" pageId="6" pageNumber="7">Japan</collectingCountry>
” is presumably mistaken (
<bibRefCitation author="Kurosawa, Y." box="[655,846,1284,1310]" pageId="6" pageNumber="7" pagination="187 - 192" refId="ref17031" refString="Kurosawa, Y. (1989) A list of the buprestid species erroneously described or recorded from Japan. Kanagawa Chuho, 90, 187 - 192." type="journal article" year="1989">Kurosawa 1989</bibRefCitation>
).
</paragraph>
